        "created_at": "2025-03-28T16:51:52.523Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Oh, I see. I didn’t think of phishing.</p>\n<p>In that case, maybe provide a more informative error message than “Invalid QR code”.</p>\n<p>First draft suggestion:<br>\n“The scanned QR is not a contact code, it is a device linking code. If you want to link to this device, go to Settings &gt; Linked devices &gt; Link a new device”.</p>",
